      "created": "2022-10-15T07:51:31.338+0000",
      "description": "The Router does not support calling SubCluster's RMAdmin directly. If we want to use management commands in Federation mode, we still need to find the Yarn client of the specified SubCluster, and then execute the Yarn management command.\r\nThis is not conducive to the unified management of Federation. The JIRA plan will enhance the router's capabilities, provide a set of CLI commands, and execute SubCluster RM management commands on the Router side.",
      "priority": {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/priority/3",
        "iconUrl": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/priorities/major.svg",
        "name": "Major",
        "id": "3"
      },
